		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">akumakuja wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">it also broke.</div><br />What the hell happened to this cart? Ruining a mask ROM isn't an easy task!<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">the pcb also has addresses A18 and A19 and my EPROM has until A17, I should do with A 18 and A19?</div><br />That's because the MMC5 supports up to 1MB of PRG, and you'r only using 256KB. Just don't connect anything to those holes.

		

